java.lang.RuntimeException
de.thm.mni.compilerbau.utils.SplError
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SplError extends RuntimeException
An exception class, that encapsulates all possible SPL errors. Contains static methods that construct exceptions for specific errors.
